00022 class type_id
00023   : public boost::less_than_comparable<type_id>
00024 {
00025 public:
00026     type_id()
00027       : id(&typeid(detail::null_type))
00028     {}
00029 
00030     type_id(std::type_info const& id)
00031       : id(&id)
00032     {}
00033 
00034     bool operator!=(type_id const& other) const
00035     {
00036         return *id != *other.id;
00037     }
00038 
00039     bool operator==(type_id const& other) const
00040     {
00041         return *id == *other.id;
00042     }
00043 
00044     bool operator<(type_id const& other) const
00045     {
00046         return id->before(*other.id);
00047     }
00048 
00049     char const* name() const
00050     {
00051         return id->name();
00052     }
00053 
00054 private:
00055     std::type_info const* id;
00056 };
